title: 03/11: Quick Reaction - Brown Trade and Hyde Signing (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We'll have our big free agency reaction show tomorrow, but let's bring on Pete Prisco to talk about Antonio Brown and Carlos Hyde! Obviously, Brown is the headliner here and we'll go over his impact on the OAK offense and what PIT will look like without him. And what role will Carlos Hyde have with KC (17:00)? How much does it hurt Damien Williams?
